item.title: Inside joke
item.dc:creator: @RancidKraut RancidKraut
item.description:
@RancidKraut wrote:

[quote=“ruler, post:14, topic:49952”][quote author=Brazen Bull link=topic=70129.msg1548705#msg1548705 date=1182943128]
I’m probably wrong, but I think this was the order of events:

  • someone was complaining about the difficulties of cheating
  • I mentioned using chimps
  • I wrote an article for it that was going to be in the next black book (which I never got around to finishing), and then posted that blured picture as a teaser
  • Kaitnieks made the banner advert

Actually, I think the joke started with Nick Sherlock. Long before autorune was created, he made a robot out of household junk and sticky tape, then photographed it.

Btw, it’s good to be here, and see so many people from kaitnieks.com.

Today someone messaged me to ask how I became a member so quickly. My reply was:

"[i]Gosh. Not only did I not realise I was a community member, I didn’t even know there was such a thing on this forum.

Sometimes I worry nobody likes me because they stare at my blouse instead of my eyes, but then they go do nice things like this :)[/i]"
[/quote]
congrats at cm with 10 rep, you are the lowest cm.[/quote]
Correction!

Erm… Never mind, I have 13.

Read full topic
